	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">为了体现蜂蜜的不同特点，他做了两种性格的包装</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-30 13:47:11 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">3</span>
		</div>
